The Keiser Report  No. 143
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 03 May 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max Keiser and co-host, Stacy Herbert, report on the $5 trillion in financial weapons for bankers and the lobbying bubble that keep those weapons flowing. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to Peter Schiff about the 'symbiotic' master-slave relationship between the U.S. and China.
